http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Governor-extends-Sankranti-greetings/article14001092.ece

Governor E.S.L. Narasimhan conveyed Sankranti festival greetings to people of Andhra Pradesh and Telangana.“On the happy occasion of Sankranti, I express my heartiest greetings to the people. The harvest festival occupies a significant place in our cultural horizon and is celebrated with all gaiety and jubilation. May this auspicious occasion inspire noble thoughts of love, affection, amity and brotherhood in us”, he stated in a press release here on Friday.Meanwhile, Andhra Pradesh Legislative Council Chairman A. Chakrapani also conveyed Sankranti greetings to people.He wished that the festival heralds a new chapter of happiness and prosperity in the lives of people of the Telugu – speaking States.